		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="351" name="FLAVORTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>The wound Broxigar dealt to Sargeras during his last stand is a glory no other orcish hero has ever achieved.</enUS>
			<zhCN>布洛克斯的临终一击伤到了萨格拉斯。这项光辉战绩在兽人英雄当中无人可及。</zhCN>
