	<Entity CardID="TIME_209" ID="119643" version="2">
		<Tag enumID="185" name="CARDNAME" type="LocString">
			<enUS>Muradin, High King</enUS>
			<zhCN>高山之王穆拉丁</zhCN>
		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="184" name="CARDTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>[x]&lt;b&gt;Fabled&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;Rush&lt;/b&gt;. &lt;b&gt;Battlecry:&lt;/b&gt;
Bring the High King's
Hammer to ME! &lt;b&gt;Deathrattle:&lt;/b&gt;
Add it to your hand.</enUS>
			<zhCN>&lt;b&gt;奇闻&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;b&gt;突袭&lt;/b&gt;。&lt;b&gt;战吼：&lt;/b&gt;为本随从装备高山之王的战锤！&lt;b&gt;亡语：&lt;/b&gt;将该战锤置入你的手牌。</zhCN>
		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="351" name="FLAVORTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>There is no story more tragic in Ironforge history than that of King Muradin slaying the corrupted Prince Arthas. The Lich King never rose to power, the Stormriders united, but the boy's death created fractures in the Alliance that would never repair.</enUS>
			<zhCN>铁炉堡的史书中最为惨痛的一笔，莫过于穆拉丁国王亲手击毙了堕落的王子阿尔萨斯。巫妖王未能崛起，驭雷者团结如初，可是王子的死还是给联盟留下了一道嫌隙，永远无法弥合。</zhCN>
		</Tag>
