			<zhCN>&lt;b&gt;奇闻&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;b&gt;抉择：&lt;/b&gt;强化辛艾萨莉；或者永恒之井。&lt;i&gt;（未选择的选项会被摧毁！）&lt;/i&gt;</zhCN>
		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="351" name="FLAVORTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>There was a time when Azshara was a benevolent queen to the Kaldorei. There is a timeline where she even stayed one.</enUS>
			<zhCN>艾萨拉曾是卡多雷一族仁善的女王。而在某条时间线中，她一直都是这样的女王。</zhCN>
		</Tag>
