		</Tag>
		<Tag enumID="351" name="FLAVORTEXT" type="LocString">
			<enUS>Whatever she would later become, no hero fought the Lich King so courageously as the Ranger General of Silvermoon.</enUS>
			<zhCN>无论她后来会变成什么样子，她都是抗击巫妖王时最为英勇的游侠将军，是银月城的英雄。</zhCN>
